##  Token Balance Agent 



This is an example Agent which responds to HTTP request from humans OR other agents as long as they pay in 'credits' using a DefiRelay Refill API Key. 


More information here :

https://defirelay.com  





### Accessing with the Indiefuture CLI 


the indiefuture CLI tool can be used to easily pay credits  in order to query this agent . 

https://github.com/indiefuture/indiefuture_cli